article.headline: Trump unveils list of Supreme Court picks that includes Cruz, other GOP senators
article.body: President Donald Trump on Wednesday unveiled a list of potential picks for the Supreme Court. The move to release a list of possible Supreme Court justices mirrors what Trump did during the 2016 presidential campaign, as he aimed to win over conservative voters who might otherwise not support him. Trump said the list released on Wednesday had 20 additions to his original list, and it included Republican Sens. Ted Cruz, Tom Cotton and Josh Hawley.
